premise_source_doc_sentence: Meira Kumar is an Indian politician and a five time Member of Parliament .
She was elected unopposed as the first woman Speaker of Lok Sabha and served from 2009 to 2014 .
She is a lawyer and a former diplomat .
Prior to being a member of the 15th Lok Sabha , she has been elected earlier to the 8th , 11th , 12th and 14th Lok Sabha .
She served as a Cabinet Minister in the Ministry of Social Justice and Empowerment of Manmohan Singh 's Congress led Government  (  2004 -- 2009  )  .
